  "detailed_description": "<h1>Blending air-combat with MOBA tower defense</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>SKYRAID is an online multiplayer game of conquest for up to 12 players. Engage in high speed aerial combat like you've never experienced it before, with a top-down camera angle, skill-based movement and combat mechanics, advanced guided weaponry and emergency countermeasures. Escort airborne forces deep into enemy territory to destroy emplacements, ships, drones, helicopters, and more.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Online Multiplayer for up to 12 players with objectives and creeps<br></li><li>Skill-based gameplay and risk-vs-reward equipment progression<br></li><li>Multiple generations of iconic fighters for you to collect and pilot from ranging from WWII propellers to modern multirole jets. (At least 25 are planned for the full release)<br></li><li>Start with props and upgrade your way to jets over the course of a single match<br></li><li>Huge variety of weapons and countermeasures to engage your enemies with<br></li><li>\"Kill-Tree\" kill-streak skill-tree to snowball your power in battle<br></li><li>Unique and vibrant art style<br></li><li>Novice / Expert control modes and Controller Support<br></li><li>Unlocked Framerate<br></li><li>Resolution independent render scaling</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/938710/extras/105107f837c5fde686ebdc8a63e087ac.avif?t=1758165074\" width=616 height=150 /></span>",
